# `any`/`all` quantifiers over a top-level array response (no auth needed for a read) — restful
# booker's `GET /booking` responds with a bare `[{"bookingid": N}, ...]` array as the whole body.

test "lists all bookings"
  api GET /booking
  expect status equals 200
  expect any body.bookingid equals 1
  expect all body.bookingid is greater than 0
